{"lastModified":1772789914386,"uri":"c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greek Islands\n\nSummer Star is our Lagoon 52, a catamaran available for crewed charters throughout Greece. With 6 cabins and 6 wc it is perfect for groups of up to 10 guests. Lengthy discussions between VPLP yacht architects known for their offshore racing cats, the world renowned Italian Nauta design agency and the leading Lagoon shipyard resulted in this game changing yacht with diamond-shaped vertical bows, beveled hulls and a Gull-wing bridge deck marking a whole new era for cruising catamarans, an eye-catcher you cannot miss! Guests get to enjoy the natural continuity and intuitive flow between the roomy, contemporary interior and the elegant exterior spaces ideally designed for entertainment and socializing! Match that with her maneuverability, sailing performance and steady handling in heavy seas and what you have is a floating dream villa offering an undisturbed sea view to Greece’s best spots!","blueprint":{"name":"SUMMER STAR","images":["/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7051e320-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71325810-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::71fa8a10-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::73d58ba0-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::72dcfad0-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cc4e71-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::74adea40-a414-11ee-a3ef-0b2547cdbcf3.